IMAPStore mailbox-remote
Host imap.mailbox.org
User caio@crthomaz.com.br
PassCmd "pass mailbox"
SSLType IMAPS

MaildirStore mailbox-local
Path ~/Mail/mailbox/
Inbox ~/Mail/mailbox/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel mailbox
Far :mailbox-remote:
Near :mailbox-local:
Patterns * !Archives
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN
User caiorulli@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass gmail"

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/Mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/Mail/gmail/INBOX
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail" !"[Gmail]/Important" !"[Gmail]/Starred" !"[Gmail]/Bin"
SyncState *
